- id: validate-operator-composition
  subject: Validate operators chained into real processor pipelines end-to-end
  status: pending
  description: |
    Witness operators composed with createProcessor and pipe():
    source -> gate -> scan -> batch pipeline producing correct output.
    mux two sources through take(5) pipeline.
    split stream into two branches with different transforms.
  effort: small
  category: infra
  blocking: []
  blockedBy: []
  acceptance:
    - gate->scan->batch pipeline produces correct batched running totals
    - mux->take produces exactly N items from merged sources
    - split branches receive identical input and transform independently
  edge_cases:
    - empty source through operator chain emits nothing
    - single-item source through batch(10) emits one batch of 1
